                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9069" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0591</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1025 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">接班人的考验：董月畅黑陶公司人才培养之困</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Troubles of the Successor: The Difficulty of Talent Training in DongYuechang Black Pottery Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李亚玲，胡媛媛，董志明</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李亚玲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李亚玲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">剑川董月畅黑陶有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">剑川黑陶；企业接班人；人才供需矛盾；人才培养模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Jianchuan Black pottery,Enterprise successor,Contradiction between the talent supply and demand,Talent cultivation mode</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">剑川董月畅黑陶有限公司位于云南大理州剑川县，由非物质文化遗产传承人董月畅创立，主要生产销售非物质文化遗产——剑川黑陶。得益于脱贫攻坚和乡村振兴，2016年董月畅的家庭小作坊华丽转身为当地黑陶产业龙头企业。本文首先介绍董月畅黑陶公司陷入人才困境的原因，公司产品、服务和销售升级引发人才需求变化；其次介绍公司人才现状与困境，详细分析人才需求类型；最后将问题聚焦在黑陶产业人才培养上，分析不同类型人才的培育策略，提出案例关键问题：非遗文化产业人才培育路径决策，引导读者分析公司人才需求变化、人才供需矛盾、人才需求特征，并对人才培育方案进行决策。通过本案例启发读者深入思考家族式非遗文化企业培育特色产业人才的路径，人才培养中如何体现“文化传承+时代价值”融合，以及如何彰显中国企业的文化传承与文化自信。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Jianchuan Dong Yuechang Black Pottery Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Dongyuechang Black Pottery Company&quot;) is located in Jianchuan,Dali,Yunnan, founded by Dong Yuechang who is an intangible cultural heritage inheritor,mainly produces and sells Jianchuan black pottery.Thanks to the poverty alleviation and rural revitalization,Dong Yuechang&#39;s small family workshop has turned into the leading enterprise in local black pottery industry in 2016.This case study first introduces the reasons why falls into the talent dilemma that the upgrading of the company&#39;s products,services and sales leads to the changing demands for talents needed.Then it introduces the current situation and dilemma of the existing talents,and analyzes types of talents needs in detail.Finally,the problem focuses on the cultivation of talents in the black pottery industry,and puts forward the key issues,namely decision-making on the cultivation path of talents in the intangible cultural heritage industry,guiding readers to analyze the changes in the company&#39;s talent demand, the contradiction between talent supply and demand,and characteristics of talent demand, further make decisions on the talent cultivation plan.Through this case,readers are encouraged to think deeply about cultivation path of characteristic industrial talents of family-owned intangible cultural heritage enterprises,and how to reflect integration characteristics of &quot;cultural inheritance&amp;times value&quot; in talents cultivation as well as demonstrate the cultural heritage and cultural confidence of Chinese enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源开发与管理》、《人力资源培训与开发》、《战略人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业者特质；人才需求；产才供需矛盾；人才培养；文化传承与创新发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
